      "data": {
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tutorial-advanced-primitives-field"
        },
        "markdown": "## Why not markdown?\n\nIf `draft` is a real status value, it belongs in a field.\n\nMarkdown can explain the value, but it should not be the value."
      }
